text: Elise Mertens and Demi Schuurs were the defending champions, but chose not to participate. Monique Adamczak and Jessica Moore won the title, defeating in the final Danka Kovinić and Vera Lapko with the score 4–6, 7–5, [10–4]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== *Main Draw Guangzhou International Women's Open - Doubles 2018 Doubles
